(3) Where, in respect of the supply of any goods , or of any service referred to in sub-section (2), payment is received or a tax invoice is issued in respect of part of the supply, paragraph (c) or (d) of that subsection shall apply to that part of the supply, and tax thereon shall be payable accordingly.
